  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To prove that video about endoscopic retrograde cholangiopancreatography (ERCP) combined with
      written informed consent provides participants more information about the procedure, which
      can make participants understand the procedure well. Investigators advocate the development
      of institutional and national guidelines to ensure optimal practices of acquiring informed
      consent.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
